  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Mashuru &amp; Kajiado Central Drought Response</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ensure functionality of existing water sources, sanitization education and disease control, and educate about environmental conservation during drought. Build shallow wells to support sanitation and ensure safe drinking water, provide school children with Vitamin A supplements and de-worming, distribute leaky tins to collect clean rain water for hand washing.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Mashuru &amp;amp; Kajiado Central response will focus on environmental conservation and the water and sanitation needs of the people</narrative>
